{"meta":{"title":"2 Nefi 22","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/22?lang=spa","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2017-11-0440-2-nephi-22-64k-spa.mp3?download=true","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"cbb5a0b12bab6289daeb6987533ad268e2d2f6aa","data-aid":"124168295","data-aid-version":"3","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/22","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"spa","data-orig-id":"9dd17b233089cb6c8ac17bf4061b02fc027c45df","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"2 Nefi 22","description":"En los días del Milenio todos los hombres alabarán al Señor — Él morará entre ellos — Compárese con Isaías 12. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"2 Nefi 22","description":"En los días del Milenio todos los hombres alabarán al Señor — Él morará entre ellos — Compárese con Isaías 12. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124168527\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 22</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124168529\" id=\"study_summary1\">En los días del Milenio todos los hombres alabarán al Señor — Él morará entre ellos — Compárese con <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/12?lang=spa\">Isaías 12</a>. Aproximadamente 559–545 a.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"111\"></span>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124168531\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Y dirás en aquel día: ¡Te alabaré, oh Señor! Aunque estabas enojado conmigo, tu ira se ha apartado, y me has consolado.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124168533\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>He aquí, Dios es mi salvación; <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>confiaré</a> y no temeré, porque el Señor <span class=\"deity-name\"><span class=\"small-caps\"><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>Jehová</a></span></span> es mi fortaleza y mi canción; y también ha llegado a ser salvación para mí.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124168535\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Por tanto, con gozo sacaréis <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>agua</a> de las fuentes de la salvación.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124168537\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span>Y en aquel día diréis: <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>¡Alabad</a> al Señor, aclamad su nombre, sus obras pregonad entre el pueblo, declarad que su nombre es ensalzado!</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124168539\" id=\"p5\"><span class=\"verse-number\">5 </span><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note5a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>¡Cantad</a> al Señor!, porque él ha hecho cosas admirables; esto es sabido por toda la tierra.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124168541\" id=\"p6\"><span class=\"verse-number\">6 </span><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note6a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>¡Da</a> voces y canta, oh moradora de Sion!, porque grande es el Santo de Israel en medio de ti.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"22\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168543\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.6?lang=spa#p6\">Mos. 4:6</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.1?lang=spa#p1\">Hel. 12:1</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note2b\" data-full-marker=\"2b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168545\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/15.2?lang=spa#p2\">Éx. 15:2</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ps/83.18?lang=spa#p18\">Sal. 83:18</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/jehovah?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Jehová</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168547\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/living-water?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Agua(s) viva(s)</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168549\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/thankful-thanks-thanksgiving?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Acción de gracias, agradecido, agradecimiento</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note5a\" data-full-marker=\"5a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124168551\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.28?lang=spa#p28\">DyC 136:28</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124169032\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/54.1?lang=spa#p1\">Isa. 54:1</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.14?lang=spa#p14\">Sof. 3:14</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2a","pid":"124168533","context":"confiaré","text":"<p data-aid=\"124168543\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" h